  <div class='flex items-stretch'>
	<div class='bg-light-blue md:px-3 px-1 lg:block hidden'>
		<div class='px-3 bg-light-cream md:w-32 w-10 overflow-hidden'>
			{{#each tile_count}}
				<img
					src='/backgrounds/latin-tile-design.png'
					alt='Latin tile design'
					class='w-full h-auto {{#if this.mobile }}lg:hidden block{{/if}}'
					width='auto'
					height='auto'
					loading='lazy'
				/>
			{{/each}}
		</div>
	</div>
	<div
		class='bg-light-cream md:pt-20 py-10 w-full max-w-[{{theme.page_width}}px] mx-auto'
	>
		<div class='flex md:px-10 px-5 md:mb-20 mb-10 lg:flex-row flex-col'>
			<div class='lg:w-3/5 w-full lg:pr-10 pr-0'>
				<h3
					class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold md:mb-10 mb-5'
				>
					Evidence-Based Models
				</h3>
				<p class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg'>
					Our facility employs a range of therapy models to provide comprehensive and personalized care to our clients. We provide 1 on 1 therapy, group therapy, and family therapy. 
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    We aim to help you on your journey to enjoy life free of substance abuse and work to correct your mental health issues. Our compassionate and skilled therapists are dedicated to supporting you toward lasting recovery and emotional well-being.
				</p>
                <img
                    src='/images/facility-img-2.jpg'
                    alt='Two men counseling'
                    class='lg:w-4/5 w-full ml-auto mr-0 h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
                    width='auto'
                    height='auto'
                    loading='lazy'
                />
			</div>
			<img
				src='/images/facility-img-1.jpg'
				alt='Hands reaching out'
				class='lg:w-2/5 w-full h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
				width='auto'
				height='auto'
				loading='lazy'
			/>
		</div>
		<div 
			class='flex md:px-10 px-5 md:mb-20 mb-10 lg:flex-row-reverse flex-col'
		>
			<div class='lg:w-3/5 w-full lg:text-right text-left'>
				<h3
					class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold md:mb-10 mb-5'
				>
					Trauma Counseling
				</h3>
				<p class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg'>
					When it comes to substance abuse, many individuals turn to drugs or alcohol as a method of coping with past traumas. Our goal is to provide support and guidance in overcoming their addictions by addressing the underlying trauma. 
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    Our dedicated team is trained to extend our resources to be tailored to your needs. This therapy approach is designed to address the unique needs of trauma victims. It helps individuals process and heal from traumatic experiences, reduces the impact of trauma-related symptoms, and fosters resilience and post-traumatic growth.
				</p>
			</div>
			<img
				src='/images/facility-img-3.jpg'
				alt='Woman giving lecture'
				class='lg:w-2/5 w-full h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8 mr-20 lg:max-h-[350px]'
				width='auto'
				height='auto'
				loading='lazy'
			/>
		</div>
		<div class='flex md:px-10 px-5 md:mb-20 mb-10 lg:flex-row flex-col'>
			<div class='lg:w-3/5 w-full lg:pr-10 pr-0'>
				<h3
					class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold md:mb-10 mb-5'
				>
					Community Housing
				</h3>
				<p class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg'>
					We offer a community housing system in connection with our facility. It will be a supervised 24/7 watch for people who need a place to stay that don’t live nearby the surrounding community.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    Amel aims to offer housing in the community so that you may continue to have a support system in your journey to sobriety.
				</p>
                <img
                    src='/images/facility-img-5.jpg'
                    alt='People packing boxes'
                    class='lg:w-4/5 w-full ml-auto mr-0 h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
                    width='auto'
                    height='auto'
                    loading='lazy'
                />
			</div>
			<img
				src='/images/facility-img-4.jpg'
				alt='Men hugging'
				class='lg:w-2/5 w-full h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
				width='auto'
				height='auto'
				loading='lazy'
			/>
		</div>
        <div 
			class='flex md:px-10 px-5 md:mb-20 mb-10 lg:flex-row-reverse flex-col'
		>
			<div class='lg:w-3/5 w-full lg:text-right text-left'>
				<h3
					class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold md:mb-10 mb-5'
				>
					PHP & IOP
				</h3>
				<p class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg'>
					Partial Hospitalization Program (PHP) and Intensive Outpatient Program (IOP) are our two pillars of treatment for our patients.
​                    <br>
                    <br>
                    PHP typically involves attending therapy sessions and receiving treatment for 25-30 hours a week. Clients return home or to a supportive living environment outside of program hours.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    IOP is a more flexible treatment option that provides a higher level of care than traditional outpatient therapy while allowing individuals to maintain their daily routines and responsibilities. This program operates 9 hours a week.  
				</p>
			</div>
			<img
				src='/images/facility-img-6.jpg'
				alt='Man offering support'
				class='lg:w-2/5 w-full h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8 mr-20 lg:max-h-[350px]'
				width='auto'
				height='auto'
				loading='lazy'
			/>
		</div>
		<div class='flex md:px-10 px-5 md:mb-20 mb-10 lg:flex-row flex-col'>
