				<h3
					class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold md:mb-10 mb-5'
				>
					Additional Services
				</h3>
				<p class='text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg'>
					In addition to traditional therapy models, we embrace holistic approaches that address the mind, body, and spirit. These may include mindfulness practices such as
                    <ul class="text-dark-green font-body md:text-2xl text-lg list-disc pl-10">
                        <li>yoga</li>
                        <li>meditation</li>
                        <li>local gym partnerships</li>
                    </ul>
				</p>
                <img
                    src='/images/facility-img-8.jpg'
                    alt='Man holding dumbbells'
                    class='lg:w-4/5 w-full ml-auto mr-0 h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
                    width='auto'
                    height='auto'
                    loading='lazy'
                />
			</div>
			<img
				src='/images/facility-img-7.jpg'
				alt='Woman doing yoga'
				class='lg:w-2/5 w-full h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
				width='auto'
				height='auto'
				loading='lazy'
			/>
		</div>
        <img
            src='/images/facility-img-9.jpg'
            alt='Group yoga'
            class='w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto h-auto md:mt-12 mt-8'
            width='auto'
            height='auto'
            loading='lazy'
        />
	</div>
	<div class='bg-light-blue md:px-3 px-1 lg:block hidden'>
		<div class='px-3 bg-light-cream md:w-32 w-10 overflow-hidden'>
			{{#each tile_count}}
